search_results.title: Brian Street (Inducted 2016)
search_results.snippet: Brian Vincent Street, professor emeritus at King's College London and visiting professor at the University of Pennsylvania, died on June 21, 2017.

search_results.title: chris street - Professor - California State University, Fullerton
